      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1622,
      "width": 889.1999999999999,
      "height": 32.5,
      "text": "Each frame the browser asks: \"did the computed value change since last frame?\" If NO → Layout & Paint are skipped.\nsteps(1,end) makes the answer \"no\" on most frames. The ease curve is baked into WHICH values the stops hold.",
      "originalText": "Each frame the browser asks: \"did the computed value change since last frame?\" If NO → Layout & Paint are skipped.\nsteps(1,end) makes the answer \"no\" on most frames. The ease curve is baked into WHICH values the stops hold.",
