      "x": 60,
      "y": 2000,
      "width": 811.1999999999999,
      "height": 32.5,
      "text": "The jumps are ~50 weight units every ~20 ms. Film is 24 fps (a new image every 42 ms) and looks smooth —\nwe step twice as fast as cinema. Same DOM, same wave, a fraction of the CPU work.",
