      "width": 429,
      "height": 65,
      "text": "← everything out here was STILL animated, shaped,\n   laid out and painted, 60×/s — you just never saw it.\n   Now each row simply stops rendering at its window\n   (+ one spare word as safety margin).",
      "originalText": "← everything out here was STILL animated, shaped,\n   laid out and painted, 60×/s — you just never saw it.\n   Now each row simply stops rendering at its window\n   (+ one spare word as safety margin).",
