      "x": 60,
      "y": 2290,
      "width": 834.6,
      "height": 32.5,
      "text": "Intro strips: rows were 60 characters long; the window can only ever show ~22.\nDelays still use each character's absolute position → the wave is pixel-identical, with 30–45% fewer spans.",
      "originalText": "Intro strips: rows were 60 characters long; the window can only ever show ~22.\nDelays still use each character's absolute position → the wave is pixel-identical, with 30–45% fewer spans.",
