      "locked": false,
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 2450,
      "width": 898.8,
      "height": 105,
      "text": "1. Can the effect be expressed with transform / opacity?  Do that — GPU handles it, main thread stays free.\n2. Must touch layout (text, width, position)?  → quantize with steps() · animate fewer elements ·\n    contain: layout style paint · pause off-screen (IntersectionObserver) · pause while scrolling.\n3. Prefer @keyframes + animation-delay over a JS requestAnimationFrame loop — zero per-frame JS.\n4. Thousands of moving things?  Leave the DOM → <canvas>. (In a Worker: load fonts via FontFace first!)\n5. Verify with DevTools → Performance (purple = Layout, green = Paint) and Rendering → Paint flashing.",
      "originalText": "1. Can the effect be expressed with transform / opacity?  Do that — GPU handles it, main thread stays free.\n2. Must touch layout (text, width, position)?  → quantize with steps() · animate fewer elements ·\n    contain: layout style paint · pause off-screen (IntersectionObserver) · pause while scrolling.\n3. Prefer @keyframes + animation-delay over a JS requestAnimationFrame loop — zero per-frame JS.\n4. Thousands of moving things?  Leave the DOM → <canvas>. (In a Worker: load fonts via FontFace first!)\n5. Verify with DevTools → Performance (purple = Layout, green = Paint) and Rendering → Paint flashing.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "containerId": null
    },
